We did it! The Priory at Landslide Lee have befriended the skritt in Kolkorensburg. We can now enter their cave and study the relics and crystal formations within. That's two things you've helped us achieve. This is an exciting day for the Priory—you have our gratitude and our thanks.

—Antal the Patient
